Title: Amazon Prime Video Business Case Study

Name: Jevin Chokshi 
Domain: Entertainment Industry
Chosen Platform: Amazon Prime Video

SECTION 1: PRODUCT DISSECTION
1. Platform Selection:
Platform Chosen: Amazon Prime

Amazon Prime Video is an online video streaming platform owned by Amazon. It allows users to watch movies, TV shows, and original content through the internet.

The platform is available in many countries and has millions of users worldwide. Prime Video is included with Amazon Prime membership, which also provides benefits such as faster delivery, music streaming, and gaming services.
I selected Amazon Prime Video because it is one of the most popular entertainment platforms and it uses data analytics to understand user preferences and recommend content. This makes it a good example for analyzing how data helps improve user experience and business growth.
2. Core Features and Functionalities:
Online Streaming: Users can watch movies and TV shows anytime through the internet without depending on television schedules.
Personalized Recommendations: The platform suggests movies and shows based on the user’s watch history and preferences.
Offline Download: Users can download movies or shows and watch them later without an internet connection.
Multiple Profiles: Users can create multiple profiles within a single account so that each user receives personalized recommendations.

3. Real World Problems Solved
Limited Access to Entertainment: Earlier people depended on television schedules. Prime Video allows users to watch content anytime.
Difficulty Finding Good Content: With thousands of movies available, users may find it difficult to choose what to watch. Prime Video solves this problem through personalized recommendations.
Device Limitations: Traditional entertainment was limited to televisions. Prime Video allows streaming on multiple devices.
Global Content Availability: Prime Video provides movies and shows from different countries, giving users access to international entertainment


